      "name": "Meet Your Designer",
      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "Meet Your Designer",
        "quote": "Most snap-on veneers are an embarrassment. I built one that isn't.",
        "body_content": "<p>Most snap-on veneers are cheaply manufactured plastic, shipped from factories by companies without a practicing dentist on the team.</p><p>Patients walk into my practice wearing them. Within a month, they stop. They're embarrassed by something they paid for.</p><p>That's the gap Revive fills. Every case is designed against my 7-Point Smile Design Protocol. <strong>If it doesn't pass, it doesn't ship.</strong> If it arrives and isn't right, we remake it. My name is on this because I built it.</p>",
        "doctor_name": "Dr. Brandon Turley, DDS",
        "doctor_title": "Doctor of Dental Surgery · Founder, Revive Teeth",
        "video": "shopify://files/videos/Dr T Intro V2(1).mp4",
        "video_caption": "Dr. Brandon Turley, DDS · 1 min 52 sec"
      }
    },
